{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/blog/the-pool-on-the-roof-must-have-a-leak","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7e881ba4-73e6-567d-a861-cea0c99ef422","html":"<p><em>This post was originally published on the <a href=\"https://whispersystems.org/blog/the-pool-on-the-roof-must-have-a-leak/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Open Whisper Systems blog</a>.</em></p>\n<p>Today we hiked the Kalalau Trail and swam beneath the cold spray of a waterfall.</p>\n<p>Today we discussed the finer points of the axolotl protocol used by TextSecure.</p>\n<p>Today we delighted in \"shave ice\", a local delicacy that is definitely <em>not</em> a snow cone.</p>\n<p>Today we wrote copy, polished features, closed bugs, and merged pull-requests.</p>\n<p>Measured by lines of code, today was short. Measured by steps taken, it was tall. Measured by ideas discussed, things learned, and sights seen, it was towering.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 675px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/a2510/falls.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Hanakapi&#39;ai Falls\"\n        title=\"Hanakapi&#39;ai Falls\"\n        src=\"/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/512c0/falls.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/2334a/falls.jpg 169w,\n/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/9c05e/falls.jpg 338w,\n/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/512c0/falls.jpg 675w,\n/static/e76cf22b0d9f68f6746e182ccea508bd/a2510/falls.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>For the past week and a half I've been trapped on an island among a team of brilliant hackers. A curious duality exists on the island. At sunrise, stand-up paddleboard yoga is followed naturally by a technical stand-up meeting. A group huddling around a laptop for hours may swiftly disband upon noticing big surf. This isn't an idle vacation, nor is it daunting contract work. We're nineteen people fervently working toward a noble goal in a stress-free mind amphitheater.</p>\n<h2 id=\"trust-on-first-use\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#trust-on-first-use\" aria-label=\"trust on first use permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Trust on first use</h2>\n<p>Coming here was a leap of faith. Before leaving, friends and family were incredulous:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>So they're going to fly you to Hawaii. And give you a surfboard. And teach you things. So that you can work on a project that you wanted to work on anyway?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Though it sounded too good to be true, sparse details soon surfaced in our inboxes:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This is your plane ticket. This is our house. This is who will pick you up.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>We arrived in Hawaii with backpacks and a vague idea of what the next two weeks would hold. The uncertainty distilled a group of self-motivated people who <em>really</em> wanted to pitch in. The lack of granular detail allowed us to fill in gaps and make the trip our own.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 675px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/a2510/shave-ice.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Kauai&#39;s Best Shave Ice\"\n        title=\"Kauai&#39;s Best Shave Ice\"\n        src=\"/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/512c0/shave-ice.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/2334a/shave-ice.jpg 169w,\n/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/9c05e/shave-ice.jpg 338w,\n/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/512c0/shave-ice.jpg 675w,\n/static/e383a57eb32914e892a97d036001dd75/a2510/shave-ice.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"an-activist-an-anarchist-and-an-astrophysicist-walk-into-a-bar\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#an-activist-an-anarchist-and-an-astrophysicist-walk-into-a-bar\" aria-label=\"an activist an anarchist and an astrophysicist walk into a bar permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>An activist, an anarchist, and an astrophysicist walk into a bar...</h2>\n<p>One of the best parts of this trip has been the conversation. The group brings a wide range of perspectives, each passionate and thoughtful. While discussing the nebulous moral code of young countries over dinner, someone asked:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Okay, but what does \"free will\" even mean?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>There was an outcry,</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"Woah, come on, don't ask a question like that!\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>a pause, then:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"we have to save <em>something</em> to talk about tomorrow!\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The most important part of an experience like this is having interesting people to share it with. On this trip, we've got 'em in spades.</p>\n<h2 id=\"body-and-mind\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#body-and-mind\" aria-label=\"body and mind permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Body and mind</h2>\n<p>Since arriving I've restructured the browser extension's event system and kayaked beside a family of sea-turtles. The day that I watched a rainstorm pass by while Lilia played ukulele was the same day that I allowed multiple conversation instances to open concurrently. If there was any uncertainty it's long gone now, replaced by a fulfillment that stretches far beyond these two weeks.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 675px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/a2510/sunset.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sunset on Kalalau Trail\"\n        title=\"Sunset on Kalalau Trail\"\n        src=\"/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/512c0/sunset.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/2334a/sunset.jpg 169w,\n/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/9c05e/sunset.jpg 338w,\n/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/512c0/sunset.jpg 675w,\n/static/79de700a5af9f64f5b04c8178e9803e5/a2510/sunset.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","fields":{"date":"January 21, 2015","slug":"/blog/the-pool-on-the-roof-must-have-a-leak","title":"The pool on the roof must have a leak"}}},"pageContext":{}}}